<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都起来吧！”悟空叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在森林里睡了一晚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧坐起来舒展了一下身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净睁开眼睛打了个哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒嘀咕道：“现在太早了，我要再睡一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒，得起来了。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开始做早饭吧。”八戒站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们每天就是干活儿。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“做饭……拿行李……走路，走路，走路！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有重要使命。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“虽然西天取经的路上有很多困难，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是大唐可以得到真经。你应该高兴才是。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简单吃过早饭后，这一行人又上路了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们穿过了一个山谷，又翻过了几座高山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午，他们正走着，突然听到有人在叫喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去好像是有人遇到麻烦了。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净点点头说：“是的，不知道发生了什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们都在这里等着。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去看一下。”悟空跳到空中四下看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到几个和尚正吃力地推着一辆车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那车里装满了巨大的石头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和尚们的表情非常痛苦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的僧袍又脏又破。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个道士站在旁边。他们穿得很好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿！”其中一个道士大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和尚们看上去很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们用力推得更快了一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么这些和尚要推那车？”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们又为什么怕那些道士呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士们走后，悟空变成了一个和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好。”悟空边说，边走近那些和尚们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们为什么要推这车啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和尚们停下来，转身看着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看上去都很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定是新来的吧？”一个和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在他们发现你以前，快点儿离开这儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“道士们控制了这里。”另一个和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸耸肩。“大家可以和平相处啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这儿不行。”第一个和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在这里会受苦的。道士们让我们做苦工。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“道士们为什么这么对你们？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“几年前，这里发生了一场旱灾。”和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“庄稼都枯死了，老百姓也都饿死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们向佛祖求雨，但是没有下雨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有一天，有个厉害的道士来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个和尚说，“他叫虎力大仙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他念咒求雨，立刻就下了大雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从此，道士们就控制了这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们毁了所有的寺院。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太可恶了。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝对不能放过那些道士。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“道士们不会永远这样对我们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个和尚说，“有一天晚上，我梦见太白金星。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说有一天有人会来救我们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是吗？”悟空扬起了眉毛说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁会来救你们？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一位厉害的猴仙。”那个和尚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他叫孙悟空。他很厉害的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他曾打败了天兵天将！”悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听说过孙悟空。他确实很厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太白金星告诉过你们他长什么样子吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，有的。”和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你们看到孙悟空，能认出他吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空说，努力忍着不笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”和尚说，“你为什么这么问？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空全身发光，变回了原形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空？”和尚们大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们立刻拜倒在地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>